06:00.229 --> 06:02.274
Sure.

06:02.318 --> 06:03.450
Okay.

06:07.497 --> 06:09.412
[sighs]

06:17.942 --> 06:20.031
[indistinct chatter]

06:25.733 --> 06:27.343
[Darnell sighs]

06:29.911 --> 06:32.479
Hey.Oh, my God. Thank you.

06:32.522 --> 06:35.395
Yeah. No problem.

06:35.438 --> 06:36.744
