the person in charge?

14:19.989 --> 14:21.643
A friend of mine

14:21.686 --> 14:23.863
told me what you guys do here.

14:23.906 --> 14:25.299
I'd be very valuable.

14:25.342 --> 14:26.735
He's all tied up right now.

14:26.778 --> 14:28.955
