14:28.998 --> 14:30.565
If that's cool.

14:33.394 --> 14:34.874
[sighs]

14:40.140 --> 14:41.489
You're the
biggest moron.

14:41.532 --> 14:43.273
I said I'll figure
something out.

14:43.317 --> 14:44.361
[sighs][sarcastically]: He's gonna
figure something out.

14:44.405 --> 14:45.536
We're totally good,
