I wish you guys could feel this.

33:35.752 --> 33:38.059
I'm made of...

33:38.103 --> 33:39.930
cloud.

33:43.586 --> 33:45.588
I feel bad.

33:46.546 --> 33:48.200
You know...

33:48.243 --> 33:51.116
I've been coming down
on you guys really hard

33:51.159 --> 33:53.379
for lying, but...

33:53.422 --> 33:54.945
the truth...

33:54.989 --> 33:56.947
is that I haven't been
no saint myself.

33:56.991 --> 33:58.558
[laughs]

33:58.601 --> 34:00.081
I've been telling
a little lie, too.

34:01.213 --> 34:02.910
Yeah?
Yeah.

34:02.953 --> 34:05.391
I do know

34:05.434 --> 34:07.567
why they never found the gun.

34:07.610 --> 34:09.830
I didn't bury it
in the woods.

34:11.005 --> 34:12.702
I hid it with Mary's.

34:12.746 --> 34:14.530
[Felix laughs]
You what?

34:14.574 --> 34:16.315
I hid it with Mary's.

34:16.358 --> 34:18.969
What does, what
does that even mean?

34:19.013 --> 34:20.232
Dude.

34:20.275 --> 34:22.408
Felix, dude.I must dance a little.

34:29.893 --> 34:31.721
[chuckles]

34:33.158 --> 34:35.508
MURPHY:
What is he doing?
Is he actually dancing?

34:35.551 --> 34:37.075
MAX: Yeah.Oh, my God.

34:37.118 --> 34:38.815
GENE:
Knew I was grasping at straws.

34:38.859 --> 34:40.556
But I really
needed something.

34:40.600 --> 34:41.992
We weren't
grasping at straws.

34:42.036 --> 34:43.385
I know she's hiding
something.

34:43.429 --> 34:44.865
Maybe she's not, Josh.

34:44.908 --> 34:47.781
And now we're right back
to where we started.

34:47.824 --> 34:49.870
[phone buzzes]

34:52.481 --> 34:54.353
I got to head to the station.
Sarah has to talk to me.

34:54.396 --> 34:56.181
Let's let 'em go.

34:56.224 --> 34:57.791
FELIX:
I realized

34:57.834 --> 35:01.186
just now that we are living
in a simulation.

35:01.229 --> 35:02.404
MURPHY:
Oh, yeah?

35:02.448 --> 35:05.494
[footfalls approaching]

35:05.538 --> 35:07.366
All right,
we're done.

35:08.845 --> 35:11.283
You guys are,
uh, free to go.

35:11.326 --> 35:14.634
♪ Born free

35:14.677 --> 35:19.204
♪ As free as the wind blows

35:19.247 --> 35:23.860
♪ As free as the grass grows

35:23.904 --> 35:27.212
♪ Born free
to follow your heart. ♪

35:27.255 --> 35:28.735
GENE:
Wait.

35:30.302 --> 35:32.130
He went in there
to steal the pills...

35:33.653 --> 35:35.307
...because he was
working for you?

35:37.047 --> 35:39.702
Look, o-obviously we still have
some kinks to work out.

35:43.184 --> 35:45.752
I was just trying to come
at Bolt from another angle.

35:45.795 --> 35:48.276
I promise you
can trust him.

35:48.320 --> 35:50.409
[door opens]

35:55.370 --> 35:57.024
She told you about me?

35:57.067 --> 35:58.199
She did.

36:01.376 --> 36:03.073
You're good to go.

36:04.379 --> 36:06.033
I took the pills out of evidence
for you and put 'em in there.

36:07.339 --> 36:08.688
Figured you might need 'em
if you're gonna get in

36:08.731 --> 36:10.777
with the Task Champ guys.

36:12.039 --> 36:14.128
Look, Sarah told me
why you're doing this.

36:14.172 --> 36:15.695
To go after
the big guys.

36:15.738 --> 36:17.218
The ones in charge,
not the runners.

36:17.262 --> 36:19.525
I promise you

36:19.568 --> 36:21.701
I'm in it for the same reason.

36:21.744 --> 36:24.443
I have no interest to take down
a bunch of kids

36:24.486 --> 36:26.271
who had no choice.

36:27.837 --> 36:28.882
And to be honest
with you, dude...

36:30.797 --> 36:32.973
...you're all I got.

36:33.016 --> 36:34.453
Look, I get you don't
want to work with me.

36:36.281 --> 36:37.978
But I promise
you'll warm up.

36:38.021 --> 36:40.023
I'm kind of impossible
not to like.

36:40.067 --> 36:42.330
At least everyone
says that.

36:52.253 --> 36:54.212
Yeah.

36:54.255 --> 36:56.214
Okay.

37:00.392 --> 37:01.784
FELIX:
I feel bad.

37:01.828 --> 37:03.525
I've been coming down

37:03.569 --> 37:05.788
on you guys really hard
for lying...

37:05.832 --> 37:07.616
There's nothing on here but
their stupid love triangle.

37:07.660 --> 37:09.792
They don't incriminate
themselves in any way.

37:09.836 --> 37:12.186
We know Felix had
a pill on him.

37:12.230 --> 37:14.406
And-and he took it.Yeah, but that's all he had.

37:14.449 --> 37:16.669
The dogs searched
every square inch of that place.

37:16.712 --> 37:19.367
FELIX:
I do know...

37:19.411 --> 37:20.847
[sighs]

37:20.890 --> 37:22.152
...why they never found the gun.

37:22.196 --> 37:23.806
I didn't bury it in the woods.

37:23.850 --> 37:25.286
I hid it with Mary's.

37:25.330 --> 37:27.593
What did he just say?[rewinding]

37:27.636 --> 37:30.335
FELIX:
I didn't bury it in the woods...

37:30.378 --> 37:32.075
Paula, it's Lesley Bell.

37:32.119 --> 37:33.990
I got you a sentence reduction

37:34.034 --> 37:35.905
in exchange for your testimony.

37:37.472 --> 37:38.952
Two years.

37:38.995 --> 37:40.519
I know, I know.

37:40.562 --> 37:42.172
Just listen.

37:42.216 --> 37:44.262
I have a plan.

37:46.481 --> 37:48.178
They'll bring you
to the D.A.'s office

37:48.222 --> 37:50.006
