There's a window
above the corner stall.

38:13.639 --> 38:14.988
I made sure it was open.

38:15.031 --> 38:16.685
And I checked the schedule.

38:16.729 --> 38:18.252
I made sure you have
a male guard,

38:18.296 --> 38:20.298
so he can't go in with you.

38:22.256 --> 38:23.605
Can I have
some privacy?

38:23.649 --> 38:25.694
There are doors.

38:54.332 --> 38:56.943
[toilet flushes]

39:05.473 --> 39:07.301
